of only three countries
in the world

00:36:30.450 --> 00:36:32.130
that recognized the
Taliban government

00:36:32.130 --> 00:36:34.570
when it ruled Afghanistan
in the 1990's.

00:36:34.570 --> 00:36:36.970
They see India as kind
of using Afghanistan

00:36:36.970 --> 00:36:39.020
to sort of encircle Pakistan.

00:36:39.020 --> 00:36:44.130
And then they have a direct
confrontation to their east.

00:36:44.130 --> 00:36:48.840
The -- a [inaudible] question
