00:36:55.530 --> 00:36:59.850
Because for all of Pervez
Musharraf's limitations

00:36:59.850 --> 00:37:02.130
as Pakistan's military
leader and president,

00:37:02.130 --> 00:37:07.110
there was a period in 2002 2003
where he was arresting a lot

00:37:07.110 --> 00:37:08.950
of al-Qaeda figures
cooperating a lot

00:37:08.950 --> 00:37:11.460
with the United States
