the, the draft?

00:39:39.370 --> 00:39:40.890
&gt;&gt; Steve Coll: It's really
interesting question.

00:39:40.890 --> 00:39:43.640
I mean you know the,
the strength

00:39:43.640 --> 00:39:47.340
of the American military as an
institution, as a journalist

00:39:47.340 --> 00:39:51.410
if you encounter it, you can
see many of its great strengths.

00:39:51.410 --> 00:39:55.660
And they're rooted in the, in
the revival of a volunteer army

00:39:55.660 --> 00:39:59.380
after the debacle of the Vietnam
War and the effects it had

00:39:59.380 --> 00:40:03.910
on the, on the military
as an institution.

00:40:03.910 --> 00:40:07.540
But I'm so struck at how
segregated the experience

00:40:07.540 --> 00:40:11.470
of sacrifice has been in both
wars because of the geography

00:40:11.470 --> 00:40:13.670
of volunteerism in the country.

00:40:13.670 --> 00:40:16.910
And I do think that a lot
of the populism and disgust

00:40:16.910 --> 00:40:18.320
that the country has expressed

00:40:18.320 --> 00:40:21.990
about its decision making
elites particularly in some

00:40:21.990 --> 00:40:24.700
of the states and
communities that volunteered

00:40:24.700 --> 00:40:28.500
to follow leaders into
these wars, is located in a,

00:40:28.500 --> 00:40:33.860
in a kind of uneven
understanding of the failures

00:40:33.860 --> 00:40:36.350
of these wars of the,
of the promises betrayed

00:40:36.350 --> 00:40:39.850
and the price paid even where
the sacrifices seen as noble.

00:40:39.850 --> 00:40:44.250
The extraordinary price that's
paid by people coming home with,

00:40:44.250 --> 00:40:47.630
with missing limbs
and, and broken spirits

00:40:47.630 --> 00:40:50.140
from repeated concussions
and so forth.

00:40:50.140 --> 00:40:55.180
So I, I'm personally
I kind of --

00:40:55.180 --> 00:40:57.950
it's not fashionable in
the zip code where I live,

00:40:57.950 --> 00:41:02.880
but I think national public
service is a, is a good policy

00:41:02.880 --> 00:41:06.010
and it doesn't have to all be
conscripted military service

00:41:06.010 --> 00:41:08.300
to be successful but these kinds

00:41:08.300 --> 00:41:10.340
of sacrifices should
not be isolated

00:41:10.340 --> 00:41:12.630
from our shared experiences.

00:41:12.630 --> 00:41:13.930
And they are.

00:41:13.930 --> 00:41:15.700
They were in this case.

