of the early debates.

00:46:35.730 --> 00:46:39.670
There were CIA people who knew
quite a lot about the resistance

00:46:39.670 --> 00:46:42.140
to the Taliban because they'd
been working with them.

00:46:42.140 --> 00:46:45.610
