the failure to see ISI go back

00:46:50.990 --> 00:46:55.960
into action until it was pretty
much too late in 2007, 2008,

00:46:55.960 --> 00:47:01.100
was partly a function of the
lack of high level understanding

00:47:01.100 --> 00:47:03.540
about the complexities
of the war

00:47:03.540 --> 00:47:05.620
and the complexities
of the region.

00:47:05.620 --> 00:47:08.170
A lot of it, more of it was
about the distraction of Iraq.

00:47:08.170 --> 00:47:09.950
But I think that was a factor.

00:47:09.950 --> 00:47:12.140
And then for those of us
who would, who would --

00:47:12.140 --> 00:47:15.290
been working on this and, and
were really engaged with it,

00:47:15.290 --> 00:47:17.040
it was frustrating
sometimes to think

00:47:17.040 --> 00:47:20.380
that our government really
didn't get it at some level.

00:47:20.380 --> 00:47:24.770
